sourcesContent:
let profileListContainer = {
  height: "22px",
  display: "flex",
  width: "calc(65vw - 28px)",
  border: "1px solid #4382BC",
  borderRadius: "5px 0px 0px 5px",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
}

let profileListContainerMain = {
  fontSize: "15px",
  textAlign: "center",
  minWidth: "200px",
  maxWidth: "200px",
  color: "white",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  lineHeight: "22px",
  borderRadius: "4px 0px 0px 4px"
}

let profileListContainerInfo = {
  width: "100%",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderLeftStyle: "none",
  borderWidth: "1px",
  borderColor: "#4382BC",
}

let profileListContainerItem = {
  fontSize: "15px",
  width: "14%",
  marginLeft: "15px",
  textTransform: "capitalize",
  overflow: "hidden",
  whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  textOverflow: "ellipsis",
  lineHeight: "20px",
  textAlign: "center",
}

export {
  profileListContainer,
  profileListContainerMain,
  profileListContainerInfo,
  profileListContainerItem,
}
